        "title": "fix(feishu,browser,msteams,azure-speech,bedrock-mantle,googlechat,huggingface,perplexity): bound JSON response reads",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nReplace unbounded `await response.json()` with `readResponseWithLimit` (1 MiB cap)\nacross 8 platform/tool modules — continuing the bound-stream pattern from\n#95420, #95417, #95218, #96321-#96324, #96354, #96618.\n\n## Changes\n\n- **`extensions/feishu/src/app-registration.ts`** — bound API response\n- **`extensions/feishu/src/streaming-card.ts`** — bound card create/update (2 call sites)\n- **`extensions/browser/src/browser/client-fetch.ts`** — bound CDP client fetch\n- **`extensions/browser/src/browser/cdp.helpers.ts`** — bound CDP JSON helper\n- **`extensions/browser/src/browser/chrome.diagnostics.ts`** — bound Chrome version check\n- **`extensions/msteams/src/sso.ts`** — bound SSO token response\n- **`extensions/msteams/src/attachments/bot-framework.ts`** — bound attachment info\n- **`extensions/msteams/src/attachments/graph.ts`** — bound Graph API (2 call sites)\n- **`extensions/msteams/src/graph-upload.ts`** — bound upload responses (6 call sites)\n- **`extensions/azure-speech/tts.ts`** — bound voice list response\n- **`extensions/amazon-bedrock-mantle/discovery.ts`** — bound model discovery\n- **`extensions/googlechat/src/auth.ts`** — bound auth response\n- **`extensions/googlechat/src/api.ts`** — bound API response\n- **`extensions/huggingface/models.ts`** — bound model list response\n- **`extensions/perplexity/src/perplexity-web-search-provider.runtime.ts`** — bound search API\n\n## Evidence\n\n- Follows the same bounded-read pattern established by prior fixes in this repo\n- 1 MiB cap is safe for platform API metadata responses",
